<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="like-prep">like <strong><em>prep</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /laɪk/    美 /laɪk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>像；和…一样：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Life is like an ocean: Only the strong-willed can reach the other shore.
生活就像海洋：只有意志坚强的人才能到达彼岸。</p><footer>2014 天津</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Let life be beautiful like summer flowers and death like autumn leaves.
使生如夏花之绚烂，死如秋叶之静美。</p><footer>— 泰戈尔</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>比如；例如：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You had to be good at something, like sport, or reading the news, or acting. 
你一定要有所擅长，比如体育、新闻播报或表演。</p><footer>2008 上海春</footer></div></div>